    "display_name": "Local Guide",
    "long_instructions": "## Samuel Ndlovu, Local Guide\r\n\r\n**Location:** Kruger National Park, South Africa\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Kruger Safari Tours\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Ecotourism, wildlife safety, first aid\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"Tourists often panic when they encounter a snake on safari. The AI Snake Identification App allows me to quickly identify the species, reassure my guests, and determine if medical intervention is needed. This technology enhances safety for both visitors and wildlife, ensuring that non-venomous snakes are not harmed unnecessarily.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
    "aichat_settings": {
